data.title: Ethereum Price Slides to $3,030 as ETF Outflows and Whale Deleveraging Dominate November
data.description: Ethereum price hurtled toward the $3,030 level on Sunday, Nov. 28, setting the asset on course to close the month with 21.4% losses. Heavy whale sell-offs in the first half of the month inflicted the most damage, as broader crypto markets reacted to the US government shutdown and political pressure ...
